First time ordering from here and I am satisfied with my order. I ordered ahead of time and my food was ready and still hot when I arrived which I loved. I got the Pure Power Plate sub the meat with a veggie burger and ordered the 1oz  Wheat Grass Shot.  The taste of the food was just okay. There really wasnt any flavor that stood out about it to be honest. However, I did drink the wheat grass shot before my meal so maybe this affected my taste a bit. The food was filling and I even had some leftover to eat later. I will order from here again. Next time I think I will try their smoothie or natural juices as they sounded really appetizing.

My friend and I came here with an offer, and because the place was fairly new, we wanted to give it a try. This place is all about eating healthy, building strength and stamina through the power of healthy food and drinks. The drinks are definitely good, since they are freshly squeezed/blended, but the food, not so much. =/ I felt like the food could have tasted so much better if everything was not already premade then mircowaved to make it warm. If I do come back, I rather get the fruit drinks instead of the food, even though they have a large selection of food on their menu.
